id: pm-f6wr
title: "Performance baseline: list-open reads all 636 items front-matter on every invocation"
description: "pm list-open takes ~4.2s for 636 items due to full front-matter scan. Evaluate cached file manifest or incremental read strategy for large corpora. Benchmark: --version ~0.8s, health ~2.5s, search ~2.3s, list-open ~4.2s, semantic reindex ~34s for 636 items."
type: Chore
status: open
priority: 3
tags[2]: performance,pm-cli
